  <title>Hints</title>

  <p><gui>Hint</gui> highlights two tiles that can be matched. If you have
  already selected one tile, it will show a match for that piece if one
  exists.</p>

  <p><gui>Hint</gui> can be accessed by pressing the <gui style="button">ðŸ’¡</gui>
  button in the header bar, or pressing <keyseq><key>Ctrl</key><key>H</key></keyseq>.</p>

  <note>
    <p><gui>Hint</gui> can make <app>Mahjongg</app> too easy, and should be used
    sparingly.</p>
    <p>There is a 30-second penalty for each use of the "hint" option.</p>
  </note>

